wifi</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> hotspot</span></li></ul></ul><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Any </span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">recommendations</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> will need to reflect on </span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">the conditions that apply in each </span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">environment – not all conclusions </span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">can or should </span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">necessarily be applicable in all environments</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-36pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">2)</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Fur</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">ther comments will be restricted to internet access in libraries</span></p><p sty